36", "resolution": "246x138"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aweqvt96058/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCNACELwBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==&rs=AOn4CLB86Rv749yQoBGqnz3FTWQwuqvyAA", "height": 188, "width": 336, "preference": -7, "id": "37", "resolution": "336x188"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aweqvt96058/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEjCNACELwBSFryq4qpAxUIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJDeAE=&rs=AOn4CLBGi3xJwcD1zo-ehlmjLcaSHkbnqg", "height": 188, "width": 336, "preference": -7, "id": "38", "resolution": "336x188"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/aweqvt96058/hqdefault.webp", "height": 360, "width": 480, "preference": -6, "id": "39", "resolution": "480x360"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aweqvt96058/sddefault.jpg", "preference": -5, "id": "40"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/aweqvt96058/sddefault.webp", "height": 480, "width": 640, "preference": -4, "id": "41", "resolution": "640x480"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aweqvt96058/hq720.jpg", "preference": -3, "id": "42"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/aweqvt96058/hq720.webp", "preference": -2, "id": "43"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aweqvt96058/maxresdefault.jpg", "height": 1080, "width": 1920, "preference": -1, "id": "44", "resolution": "1920x1080"}, {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/aweqvt96058/maxresdefault.webp", "height": 1080, "width": 1920, "preference": 0, "id": "45", "resolution": "1920x1080"}], "thumbnail": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/aweqvt96058/maxresdefault.webp", "description": "The ICICI Lombard Family Shield Personal Accidental Insurance Policy is a comprehensive policy that provides financial protection for you and your family in the event of an accidental death or disability. This policy covers you against a variety of risks, including:\n\n\n\nAccidental death\nPermanent total disability (PTD)\nAccidental hospitalization\nAccidental hospital daily allowance\nThe policy also offers a number of benefits, including:\n\n\nFinancial security for your family in the event of your accidental death or disability\nReimbursement of accidental hospitalization expenses\nDaily allowance to cover living expenses during accidental hospitalization\nThe ICICI Lombard Family Shield Personal Accidental Insurance Policy is ideal for anyone who wants to protect themselves and their family from the financial consequences of an accident. This includes salaried individuals, self-employed individuals, students, homemakers, and retirees.\n\n\nHere are some of the key features of the ICICI Lombard Family Shield Personal Accidental Insurance Policy:\n\n\nFlexible coverage options: You can choose the sum insured and coverage options that best suit your needs and budget.\nAffordable premiums: The premiums for the ICICI Lombard Family Shield Personal Accidental Insurance Policy are very affordable.\nEasy to buy: You can buy the policy online or through an ICICI Lombard insurance agent.\nClaim settlement ratio: ICICI Lombard has a very good claim settlement ratio, which means that you can be confident that your claim will be settled quickly and efficiently.\nIf you are looking for a comprehensive and affordable personal accidental insurance policy, the ICICI Lombard Family Shield Personal Accidental Insurance Policy is a good option to consider.\n\n#icici #icicilombard #investmart #healthinsurance #health #financialfreedom #financialplanning \n\n\nGoogle form-:https://forms.gle/pwd88dawoZ4fGJsg9\nPolicy wording: https://irdai.gov.in/documents/37343/931203/ICIHLIP22092V032122_HEALTH2105.pdf/a9f5172f-839f-84e7-dfa4-df80a27c0c0c?version=1.1&t=1668843142555&download=true\n\n\n📞Contact us at: +91 92162 71115\nvisit our website : www.investmartadvisory.com\n\n\n\n\n________________________________________________________________________________________________\nDisclaimer : Information presented in this video is for educational purpose only. It may not necessarily be taken as financial, legal or any other type of advice. It is not as per individual needs, objectives or financia